{"tid":1401900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鍾馗教路] 100%防到前線有鬼嘅方法！毫無破綻！","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:35:16.000Z","uid":218570,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e82cf3d51282eedb58a8be5f853a7b44bac78b01","tid":1401900,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:19:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">TLDR:發夢時 100%尊重前線決定<br />\n發夢前後 希望前線多角度思考 多聽意見</span><br />\n<br />\n眼見好多人都屌話前線有鬼 係有可能 不過<br />\n我地唔能夠倒退返去五年前雨傘果陣<br />\n陷入不停捉鬼 自我消耗嘅陷阱<br />\n呢樣係<span style=\"color: violet;\">對家最想見到</span>嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n同公海一樣 咁多萬個示威者入面<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定有狗有鬼</span></span><br />\n我地無可能會捉得哂 亦唔可以自亂陣腳<br />\n回想返呢兩個月以黎 點解我地仲有得打？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為集體智慧</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">我地有比毅進狗更高嘅智慧<br />\n我地信奉不割蓆 不分化<br />\n我地會虛心接受其他人嘅意見<br />\n我地100%尊重前線決定<br />\n所以先可以去到今日</span><br />\n<br />\n但 前線同所有抗爭者一樣 都有<span style=\"color: orange;\">思考盲點</span><br />\n所有人嘅決定都唔係100%啱<br />\n加上鬼係捉唔哂嘅 我地係要預防有鬼<br />\n而方法只有一個 <span style=\"color: red;\">集體智慧</span><br />\n鬼係好難影響到呢樣野嘅<br />\n所以我懇請前線做任何決定之前<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">諗一諗要達到嘅目的<br />\n思考大家發夢前討論嘅野</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果要守 點解要守？<br />\n呢幾日講嘅遊擊戰係咪適合啲？<br />\n紅隧果邊撚完狗就走係咪好啲？<br />\n而家重點係咪大三罷？如果係嘅 係咪應該留力？<br />\n如果有心理準備被捕 值唔值得？<br />\n現階段仲需唔需要民意戰？定係要hit&amp;run?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家禮貌地表達意見<br />\n真正嘅不割蓆 不分化 <br />\n係尊重 理解所有人嘅意見同決定<br />\n而唔係盲目信奉某班人 某種諗法<br />\n咁樣同大台 同教條主義冇分別<br />\n一定要記住自己係會出錯嘅<br />\n我地嘅優勢 係思想上Be water</span></span><br />\n<br />\n天佑我城 抗爭到底<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFFLEm9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFFLEm9.gif&h=1a5552ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e77b55cb47bb69680e1cc900a1fac269e04c5d53","tid":1401900,"uid":218570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標為本 小心翻盤<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"879e067999018bc7404b7102c35793ef0136b7ff","tid":1401900,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:25:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標為本 小心翻盤<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3745ce824ac135238560b0f4619e9dd971d312a3","tid":1401900,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標為本 小心翻盤<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"355d65a8ebb27bbfea6e30b8a71075034ef7e4a0","tid":1401900,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:31:02.000Z","msg":"九龍城新蒲崗手足, 你地全程比TVB臥底跟曬播live喇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dveJQT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dveJQT</a><br />\n<br />\n前線真係有鬼"},{"pid":"043ac07d39b81d8ed7098273fa972956a3dbb1ee","tid":1401900,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標為本 小心翻盤<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"bd8b8525982fc29534e6c001639b09c27536c759","tid":1401900,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:34:36.000Z","msg":"正式宣佈 要屌鬼嘅屌到十二點就好 之後一齊檢討返今日行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1401538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1401538</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b57c4e84634e16eeb4a7c677fbbc88bb9dead493","tid":1401900,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全部同我入去睇攻略備戰聽日港島西戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif